               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_fff8261b1d53c86d7ab0b67805e31cd0">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes: Petition of Dunbar to Gov. Carondelet, the original note, Carondelet's orders, proceedings, and power of attorney from Dunbar to F. Deverget Sansovel.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
            <c id="ref12" level="file">
